Appendix C Examination of this data set, which is limited to the planning area or immediate surrounding lands, will allow us to evaluate the applicability of the late-successional forest structural characteristics used in this analysis and might lead to refinement of the threshold levels.
Although this more local data set is not yet fully compiled, preliminary examination suggests that it is substantially similar to the Poage data set and will not lead to any substantial modifications of the late-successional forest structural characteristic thresholds in this analysis.
